<body>
  <h1>Delete Your Xpenzora Account</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>1. How to Delete Your Account</h2>
    <p>You can permanently delete your account and all associated data directly from within the Xpenzora app by following these steps:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Login to your account and go to the <strong>Home Screen</strong>.</li>
      <li>Tap on the <strong>Delete Account</strong> button.</li>
      <li>On the Deletion Screen:
        <ul>
          <li>Enter your account password to confirm your identity.</li>
          <li>Type <strong>DELETE</strong> into the confirmation text field.</li>
          <li>Press the <strong>Delete</strong> button.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Your account and all associated data will be permanently removed from our servers.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. If You Cannot Access the App</h2>
    <p>If you are unable to log in or access the Xpenzora app but still want your account deleted, please contact us using your registered email address:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@xpenzora.com">support@xpenzora.com</a></p>
    <p>We will verify your request and process the deletion within 7 days.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. Important Notes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Deleting your account is <strong>permanent</strong> and cannot be undone.</li>
      <li>All business data, transactions, images, and team information linked to your account will also be deleted.</li>
      <li>If you reinstall the app or sign up again, you will need to create a new account.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

